36
00:03:41,971 --> 00:03:44,849
I think we should station more guards
with Ms. Jang.

37
00:03:45,516 --> 00:03:47,143
You know, it was stolen once...

38
00:03:47,226 --> 00:03:49,729
Don't mention what happened in the past.
You might jinx it.

39
00:03:52,064 --> 00:03:53,064
I'm sorry.

40
00:03:53,566 --> 00:03:57,278
I'm just bothered by what that prosecutor
is up to these days.

41
00:03:57,904 --> 00:03:59,739
